title: Hour 2 - NFL Fans Are Spoiled, Albert Breer
itunes:title: Hour 2 - NFL Fans Are Spoiled, Albert Breer
description:
Ross Tucker is filling in for Dan Patrick and he is amazed at NFL fans constantly complaining that every prime-time game isn't great. And he talks to NFL insider Albert Breer who says the Tampa Bay Buccaneers are starting to look their age.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
